Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
gui_schematic_load_view(25.10)                  gui_schematic_load_view(25.10)

Name
       gui_schematic_load_view - Loads the specified schematic file

Syntax
       gui_schematic_load_view

       [-help]

       -file <file_name>[-name <name>]

       Loads the specified schematic file.

       This commands work only in the cone view (flattened mode).

Parameters
       -help  Prints  a  brief description of the gui_schematic_load_view com-
              mand.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man  command:
              man gui_schematic_load_view.

       -file <file_name>
              Specifies the name of the schematic file to be loaded.

       -name <name>
              Specifies a unique window name for the opened schematic view.

Related Information
              * gui_schematic_save_view

